Flower Watering with GL Embedded Starter Kit

This is a simple implementation of flower watering
device with climate control and hazardous gases
detector, connected to the Internet and accessible
through Mozilla IOT gateway on RaspberryPi.

The Flower Waterer is developed for GL Embedded Starter Kit
and demonstrates ideas that can be realized by students
during education process

This project can be imported to System Workbench for STM32 IDE,
built and flashed to GL Embedded Starter Kit board

